        Your BAP talks to the network. The network sends every request to
        your BPP. Your BPP demultiplexes by <code>provider_id</code> and
        hands the call off to the right store's backend. Each store then
        runs its own fulfilment — its own warehouse, its own courier (or
        in-house driver), its own door-to-door delivery.
      </p>

